      <div class="arch-diagram-hint">Scroll horizontally to inspect the full system →</div>
      <div class="arch-diagram-legend" aria-label="Diagram legend">
        <span><i></i>Production flow</span><span><i class="is-amber"></i>Policy / authority</span><span><i class="is-red"></i>Failure and repair loop</span><span><i class="is-dashed"></i>Supporting dependency</span>
